{"id":620300,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/pcm-订阅数过亿youtuber-pewdiepie-发言支持香港抗争者/","date":"2019-10-17T22:41:52Z","modified":"2019-10-17T22:41:52Z","title":"PCM | 订阅数过亿YouTuber PewDiePie 发言支持香港抗争者","content":"<p>反送中抗争至今近四个月，不论是支持或反对一方都各持其见，而不少知名人物也发声表达自己的意见。于全球订阅数超过一亿、目前排行第二的YouTuber 「 PewDiePie 」近日发布影片表示支持香港抗争者，并对近期中美冲突发表评论。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_620303\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/pewdiepie-100-million-youtube.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-620303\" class=\"wp-image-620303\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/pewdiepie-100-million-youtube.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"307\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/pewdiepie-100-million-youtube.jpg 1140w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/pewdiepie-100-million-youtube-300x184.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/pewdiepie-100-million-youtube-768x472.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/pewdiepie-100-million-youtube-1024x629.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/pewdiepie-100-million-youtube-1080x663.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-620303\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">于全球订阅数超过一亿，目前排行第二的YouTuber 「 PewDiePie 」。</p></div>\n<p><span>PewDiePie于影片「 Hong Kong vs Joker Ends Fortnite 」中，以他平时作为娱乐型YouTuber的风格，透过轻松的内容由浅入深讲解反送中抗争。透过「</span><a title=\"「 Free Hong Kong 」的纸板被「暴雪」将纸板抢走。\" href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/10/15/fortnite%E9%BB%91%E6%B4%9E%E7%B5%90%E5%B1%80%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E5%81%9C%E6%A9%9F%E4%BA%8C%E5%A4%A9-%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E7%88%AD%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%91%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>《 Fortnite 》黑洞事件</span></a><span>」及电影《小丑》的Memes（迷恩）等热门内容开始话题。当他说到「其实除了10个Memes外，其实我还有第11个《小丑》 Memes 」，后来当出现一张讽刺</span><a title=\"「 Free Hong Kong 」的纸板被「暴雪」将纸板抢走。\" href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/10/08/%e3%80%8a%e7%88%90%e7%9f%b3%e6%88%b0%e8%a8%98%e3%80%8b%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e9%81%b8%e6%89%8b%e5%8f%ab%e3%80%8c%e5%85%89%e5%be%a9%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e3%80%8d%e3%80%80%e8%a2%ab%e7%bd%b0%e6%b2%92%e6%94%b6/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>香港电竞选手被暴雪禁赛</span></a><span>的影片（约11分钟29秒），主角拿住一个写住「 Free Hong Kong 」的纸板，然后被一个标记了「暴雪」标志的人将纸板抢走。</span></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_620304\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-620304\" class=\"wp-image-620304\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"277\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual.jpg 1200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-300x166.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-768x426.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-1024x567.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-1080x599.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-620304\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">「 Free Hong Kong 」的纸板被标记了「暴雪」标志的人将纸板抢走，除了聪哥事件外，亦暗喻早前同理由被禁赛的美国大学队伍。</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_620305\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-1.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-620305\" class=\"wp-image-620305\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"285\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-1.jpg 1200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-1-300x171.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-1-768x437.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-1-1024x583.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-1-1080x615.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-620305\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">讲到香港与中国的关系时， PewDiePie 则拿出《宠物小精灵》中关都地区的地图出来（其外型与香港十分相似），用容易入口的方式去让观众代入。</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_620306\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-3.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-620306\" class=\"wp-image-620306\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"306\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-3.jpg 1200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-3-300x167.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-3-768x428.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-3-1024x570.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-3-1080x601.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-620306\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">亦有展示出香港抗争者的照片去讲解</p></div>\n<p>PewDiePie 开始在影片讲解反送中抗争的起因，当讲到香港的现况时，他以「 Hong Kong is a semi-autonomous state of China, they have their own legal system…. Hong Kong wants to be free. 」 （香港是中国的半自治区，它们有自己的法律制度。香港希望自由）去形容。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_620307\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/002-2.png\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-620307\" class=\"wp-image-620307\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/002-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"313\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/002-2.png 1200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/002-2-300x188.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/002-2-768x480.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/002-2-1024x640.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/002-2-400x250.png 400w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/002-2-1080x675.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-620307\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">暴雪近来引发的事件令不少玩家失望</p></div>\n<p>对于「聪哥事件」的相关惩处，他表示则「 China&#8217;s just like the one person on twitter that can&#8217;t take any criticism and just blocks everyone…… because Blizzard needs Chinese money！（中国就像Twitter 上一个不能接受任何批评的用家，只会封锁其他用家⋯⋯因为暴雪需要中国人的钱！）」，并提到中国是暴雪一个极大的资金来源，不论手机或PC 游戏多数都是中国玩家为主，因此他们会主动配合中方的要求，如将游戏内容或敏感政府题材「和谐」。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_620308\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-4.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-620308\" class=\"wp-image-620308\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"276\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-4.jpg 1200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-4-300x166.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-4-768x424.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-4-1024x566.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-4-1080x597.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-620308\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">有玩家暴雪旗下游戏《 Overwatch 》中人物「小美」改成声援香港的形象，令大量中国玩家暴怒。</p></div>\n<p>就此事件PewDiePie 批评游戏公司「 At the end of the day, their goal is to make money, they don&#8217;t care about you and freedom… At least people push back to the company, they are not going to do anything （归根结底，游戏公司目标是赚钱，它们不在乎你和自由⋯⋯至少人们会把责任推回游戏公司，但他们不会做任何事情。 ）」，去形容企业以钱为重，却无视企业社会责任。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_620309\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-2.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-620309\" class=\"wp-image-620309\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"280\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-2.jpg 1200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-2-300x168.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-2-768x431.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-2-1024x574.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/ProjectA_visual-2-1080x606.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-620309\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">抨击中国的Meme 难免会有习近平的出现</p></div>\n<p><span>PewDiePie于影片中以中国打压NBA 、</span><a href=\"https://www.playit.hk/%e6%ad%a3%e5%bc%8f%e8%b7%aa%e4%bd%8e%ef%bc%9f%e3%80%8a%e5%8d%97%e6%96%b9%e5%85%ac%e5%9c%8b%e3%80%8b%e8%a3%bd%e4%bd%9c%e7%b5%84%e7%82%ba%e6%96%b0%e4%b8%80%e9%9b%86%e3%80%8c%e9%81%93%e6%ad%89%e3%80%8d/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>《南方公国》 Band in China</span></a><span>  及「习维尼」等容易理解的中美冲突内容，去让大众去理解反送中抗争，也许这样的方式未必令初次接触抗争的网民了解完整事情，但如果能够令一部分观众转为更关注中国与其他地区发生的磨擦，也未尝不是个好方法。</span></p>\n<p><span>由于影片内容过多未能尽录，有兴趣观看影片的读者可</span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OhWZavn2OvM&amp;fbclid=IwAR0NsJahx_d5S3dGrrsvqhbvkQ1vg4Mm2kJmvKxKNLzxKKPcEFZ4JNmkxXw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-rel=\"lightbox-video-0\"><span>按此</span></a><span>收看。</span></p>\n<p><iframe title=\"Hong Kong vs Joker Ends Fortnite\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OhWZavn2OvM?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":974,"categories":[18271,38908,38955],"tags":[39130,39131,39035,38564,38968]}